## Technical SEO

### 1. Sitemap (sitemap.ts)
- Must include all public pages
- Update automatically when new posts added
- Include `lastModified`, `changeFrequency`, `priority`
- Support all locales (th, en)

### 2. Robots.txt (robots.ts)
- Allow all user-agents by default
- Disallow `/api/`, `/_next/`
- Point to sitemap location

### 3. URL Structure
- Clean, readable URLs: `/en/post/meditation-basics`
- Include locale in path: `/{locale}/...`
- Use slugs, not IDs when possible
- Lowercase, hyphen-separated

