## Content Optimization

### 1. Headings (H1-H6)
- One H1 per page (page title)
- Use H2-H6 for structure
- Include keywords naturally in headings
- Maintain logical hierarchy

### 2. Keywords
- Primary keyword in: H1, first paragraph, meta title/description
- Use related keywords (LSI) throughout
- Avoid keyword stuffing (write naturally)
- Include keywords in image alt text

### 3. Internal Linking
- Link to related posts/pages
- Use descriptive anchor text (not "click here")
- Maintain logical site structure
- Help users navigate related content

