## Images

### 1. Optimization
- Use Next.js `<Image>` component (automatic optimization)
- Always include `alt` attribute (describe image for SEO + accessibility)
- Provide `width` and `height` or use `fill` with `sizes`
- Use modern formats (WebP via Next.js optimization)

### 2. Alt Text
- Descriptive but concise (5-10 words)
- Include relevant keywords naturally
- Don't start with "Image of..." (implied)

Example:
```tsx
<Image
  src={post.imageUrl}
  alt={post.title}
  width={1200}
  height={600}
  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px"
/>
```

