## Multi-Language (i18n)

### 1. Structure
- Each locale has separate content: `/th/`, `/en/`
- Default locale: `en` (global audience)
- Support locale in all dynamic routes

### 2. Content
- Translate all UI text via dictionaries
- Keep separate markdown files per locale
- Maintain consistency in topics across languages

### 3. Metadata
- Translate title/description per locale
- Use appropriate language-specific keywords

