## Tools & Monitoring

1. **Google Search Console** — Track rankings, errors, indexing
2. **Sitemap submission** — Submit `/sitemap.xml` to GSC
3. **Page Speed Insights** — Test performance
4. **Lighthouse** — Audit SEO, performance, accessibility

