## Do Not

- ❌ Use generic titles like "Blog Post | Serene Mind"
- ❌ Duplicate meta descriptions across pages
- ❌ Keyword stuff (unnatural repetition)
- ❌ Hide text for SEO (cloaking)
- ❌ Ignore mobile optimization
- ❌ Create thin content (< 300 words without value)
- ❌ Use auto-generated content without review
